text: Nad Narimani (born April 14, 1987) is an English mixed martial artist. He was the formal Cage Warriors Fighting Championship featherweight champion and he competed in the Featherweight division of the Ultimate Fighting Championship. == References == Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:British mixed martial artists Category:Sportspeople of Iranian descent Category:Iranian mixed martial artists Category:Sportspeople from Bristol Category:Mixed martial artists utilizing jujutsu Category:Mixed martial artists utilizing Brazilian jiu-jitsu Category:Featherweight mixed martial artists Category:Ultimate Fighting Championship male fighters Category:English practitioners of Brazilian jiu-jitsu Category:Iranian practitioners of Brazilian jiu-jitsu Category:People awarded a black belt in Brazilian jiu- jitsu
